{"title":"开关灯","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1690","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>    YYX家门前的街上有N(2&lt;=N&lt;=100000)盏路灯，在晚上六点之前，这些路灯全是关着的，六点之后，会有M(2&lt;=m&lt;=100000)个人陆续按下开关，这些开关可以改变从第i盏灯到第j盏灯的状态，现在YYX想知道，从第x盏灯到第y盏灯中有多少是亮着的(1&lt;=i,j,x,y&lt;=N)</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<div>第 1 行: 用空格隔开的两个整数N和M</div>\n<div>第 2..M+1 行: 每行表示一个操作, 有三个用空格分开的整数: 指令号(0代表按下开关，1代表询问状态), x 和 y </div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>第 1..询问总次数 行:对于每一次询问，输出询问的结果</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>4 5<br>0 1 2<br>0 2 4<br>1 2 3<br>0 2 4<br>1 1 4<br><br></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<div><span>1<br>2</span></div>\n<div><span><br></span></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一共4盏灯，5个操作，下面是每次操作的状态(X代表关上的，O代表开着的)：</p>\n<p>XXXX -&gt; OOXX -&gt; OXOO -&gt; 询问1~3 -&gt; OOXX -&gt; 询问1~4</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}